OL,6,FBenefit cheat Adrian Cooper duped
OL,7,Ftaxpayers out of more than #57,000
OL,8,Fbenefits - after claiming he did not
OL,9,Fknow his wife had a job.
OL,11,FThe 57-year-old received income
OL,12,Fsupport, jobseekers allowance and
OL,13,Fhousing benefit.
OL,15,FBut heard he was not entitled to the
OL,16,Fmoney as his wife worked and he failed
OL,17,Fto declare he had a part-time job at .
