OL,6,FIn his interview, Cooper stated he was
OL,7,Funaware his spouse was in employment
OL,8,Fdespite her leaving the house at 8am
OL,9,Fand returning at 5pm each day.
OL,11,FIn total he claimed #57,774.46 he was
OL,12,Fnot entitled to between March 31, 2009
OL,13,Fand January 14, 2019.
OL,15,FNow Cooper has been sentenced to 34
OL,16,Fweeks in prison, suspended for 18
OL,17,Fmonths.
