OL,6,FShe said: "But he failed to inform
OL,7,Fthat his wife was working. He was also
OL,8,Fearning a small amount at a working
OL,9,Fmen's club in Newcastle. His wife was
OL,10,Fearning #100 a week.
OL,12,F"The defendant stated in his interview
OL,13,Fthat he was unaware she was in
OL,14,Femployment. But she was leaving at 8am
OL,15,Fand returning at 5pm.
OL,17,F"He said his income did not exceed the
OL,18,Famount he needed to disclose. He said
OL,19,Fit was less than #40 a week."
