OL,6,FCooper, of Albermarle Road, Newcastle,
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to two charges of
OL,8,Fdishonestly failing to disclose
OL,9,Finformation and two charges of fraud.
OL,11,FRepresenting himself Cooper said: "I
OL,12,Faccept responsibility. I have never
OL,13,Fdone anything wrong in my life.
OL,15,F"I was working at Newcastle Working
OL,16,FMen's Club. I was told it did not need
OL,17,Fto be declared."
OL,19,FHe added he stopped working at the
OL,20,Fworking men's club in 2019.
