OL,7,FCooper must complete a rehabilitation
OL,8,Factivity requirement for 30 days.
OL,10,FDistrict Judge Ian Barnes said: "It
OL,11,Frelated to a number of different types
OL,12,Fof benefits.
OL,14,F"During the years of these claims you
OL,15,Fcompleted numerous forms stating the
OL,16,Fposition was still the same. But the
OL,17,Freality was your wife was working. She
OL,18,Fwas earning.
OL,20,F"You were also earning.
